response.original_title: David Bowie A Divine Symmetry An alternative journey through Hunky Dory
response.overview: DAVID BOWIE DIVINE SYMMETRY (4CD/Blu-ray)a four-CD celebrates the twelve months running up to the release of the album HUNKY DORY in December 1971 via home demos, BBC radio sessions and live and studio recordings.  DAVID BOWIE DIVINE SYMMETRY contains 48 previously unreleased tracks/demos from the period, and new alternative mixes of HUNKY DORY tracks by original co-producer Ken Scott.
response.title: David Bowie A Divine Symmetry An alternative journey through Hunky Dory
